\c 22
\s Rwiyo rwaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakataura kuna Jehovha mashoko orwiyo urwu nenguva yaakarwirwa naJehovha pamaoko avavengi vake vose, napamaoko aSauro;
\v 2 akati,
\s "Jehovha idombo rangu, nenhare yangu,
\s nomurwiri wangu, iye ndowangu.
\p
\v 3 Mwari idombo rangu, ndichavimba naye;
\s Nhoo yangu, norunyanga
\s rwokuponeswa kwangu, shongwe yangu
\s yakakwirira, soutiziro hwangu. Muponesi wangu, anondiponesa pakumanikidzwa.
\p
\v 4 Ndichadana kuna Jehovha, iye
\s anofanira kurumbidzwa;
\s Naizvozvo ndichaponeswa kuna vavengi vangu.
\p
\v 5 "Nokuti mafungu orufu
\s akandikomba,
\s Uye nzizi dzezvakaipa
\s dzakandivhundusa.
\p
\v 6 Mabote aSheori akandisunga, Misungo yorufu yakandiwira.
\p
\v 7 "Pakutambudzika kwangu
\s ndakadana kuna Jehovha,
\s Ndakadana kuna Mwari wangu, Akanzwa izwi rangu ari mutemberi yake;
\s Kuchema kwangu kukasvika
\s munzeve dzake.
\p
\v 8 "Ipapo nyika yakazununguka, ikadedera;
\s Nheyo dzokudenga
\s dzakadengenyeka,
\s Dzikazununguswa, nokuti iye wakanga atsamwa.
\p
\v 9 Utsi hwakakwira hwuchibva mumhino dzake,
\s Uye moto wakabuda mumuromo make, wakaparadza;
\s Mazimbe akabatidzwa nawo.
\p
\v 10 Wakakotamisawo kudenga-denga, akaburuka,
\s Nerima guru rakanga riri pasi petsoka dzake.
\p
\v 11 Wakatasva kerubhu, akabhururuka; Zvirokwazvo, wakaonekwa ari pamapapiro emhepo.
\p
\v 12 Wakazvipoteredza nerima setende, Mvura yakaunganidzwa, nemvumi dzehore dzedenga.
\p
\v 13 Nokupenya, kwakanga kuri pamberi pake,
\s Mazimbe omoto akabatidzwa.
\p
\v 14 Jehovha wakatinhira kudenga, Wokumusoro-soro wakataura nezwi rake.
\p
\v 15 Wakatuma miseve, akavaparadza; Akatuma mheni, akavavhundusa.
\p
\v 16 Ipapo pasi pegungwa pakaonekwa, Uye nheyo dzenyika dzakaratidzwa pachena,
\s Nokutuka kwaJehovha,
\s Nokufema kwemweya wemhino dzake.
\p
\v 17 "Wakatambanudza ruoko rwake ari kumusoro, akanditora, Akandinyukura pamvura zhinji;
\p
\v 18 Akandirwira pamuvengi wangu ane simba,
\s Nokuna vanondivenga; nokuti vakanga vondikurira.
\p
\v 19 Vakandivinga nezuva renjodzi yangu,
\s Asi Jehovha wakanga ari mutsigiro wangu.
\p
\v 20 Akandibudisira kunzvimbo yakafarikana,
\s Akandirwira, nokuti wakanga achindifarira.
\p
\v 21 "Jehovha wakandiitira zvakaenzana nokururama kwangu,
\s Akandipa mubayiro wakaenzana
\s nokuchena kwamaoko angu.
\p
\v 22 Nokuti ndakachengeta nzira dzaJehovha,
\s Handina kubva kuna Mwari wangu nokunyengera.
\p
\v 23 Nokuti zvose zvaakatonga
\s zvakanga zviri pamberi pangu; Kana zviri zvaakatema, handina kutsauka kwazviri.
\p
\v 24 Ndakanga ndakarurama kwazvo pamberi pake, Ndakazvichengeta pazvakaipa
\s zvangu.
\p
\v 25 Naizvozvo Jehovha wakandiitira zvakaenzana nokururama kwangu, Zvakaenzana nokuchena kwangu
\s pamberi pake.
\p
\v 26 "Ane ngoni, munomuitirawo ngoni; Munhu, wakarurama kwazvo, munomuitirawo zvakarurama;
\p
\v 27 Wakanaka, munomuitirawo zvakanaka;
\p Wakatsauka, munomuitira hasha.
\v 28 Muchaponesa vanhu
\s vanotambudzika,
\s Asi meso enyu anoona
\p vanozvikudza kuti muvaderedze.
\v 29 Nokuti muri mwenje wangu, Jehovha;
\s Jehovha uchavhenekera rima rangu.
\p
\v 30 Nokuti nemi ndichavamba hondo, Kana ndina Mwari wangu
\s ndichadarika rusvingo.
\p
\v 31 "Kana ari Mwari, nzira yake yakarurama kwazvo;
\s Shoko raJehovha rakaidzwa; Ndiye nhoo yavose vanotenda kwaari.
\p
\v 32 Nokuti ndianiko Mwari, asi iye Jehovha?
\s Ndianiko dombo, asi iye Mwari wedu?
\p
\v 33 Mwari ndiye nhare yangu ine simba;
\s Iye unondifambisa nenzira yakarurama.
\p
\v 34 Unoita tsoka dzangu setsoka dzenondokadzi,
\s Unondiisa pakakwira.
\p
\v 35 Unodzidzisa maoko angu kurwa; Naizvozvo maoko angu
\s anowembura uta hwendarira.
\p
\v 36 "Makandipawo nhoo yokuponesa kwenyu,
\s Unyoro hwenyu hwakandikurisa.
\p
\v 37 Makandiitira nzvimbo
\s yakafarikana pasi pangu pandingatsika;
\s Tsoka dzangu hadzina kutedzemuka.
\p
\v 38 Ndakateverera vavengi vangu, ndikavaparadza,
\s Handina kudzokazve kusvikira vapedzwa.
\p
\v 39 Ndakavapedza, ndakavabaya, havagoni kumuka;
\s Vakawira pasi petsoka dzangu.
\p
\v 40 Nokuti makandisunga chiwuno
\s nesimba rokurwa naro; Makandikundisa vaindimukira.
\p
\v 41 Makatizisa vavengi vangu, Kuti ndiparadze vanondivenga.
\p
\v 42 Vakatarira, asi kwakanga kusino muponesi,
\s Kuna Jehovha, asi haana kuvapindura.
\nb
\v 43 INpo thaapw any a-pwanya seguruva renyika;
\s Ndikavaswa samatope enzira dzomumusha,
\p ndikavaparadzira kure.
\v 44 "Makandirwirawo
\s pakukakavadzana kwavanhu vangu,
\s Makandichengeta kuti ndive mukuru wendudzi;
\s Vanhu vandakanga ndisingazivi, vachandishumira.
\p
\v 45 Vatorwa vachanamata kwandiri; Vachateerera pakarepo kana vachindinzwa.
\p
\v 46 Vatorwa vachatorerwa simba, Vachabuda pavaivanda vachidedera.
\p
\v 47 "Jehovha mupenyu; dombo rangu ngarikudzwe;
\s Mwari, dombo rokuponeswa
\s kwangu, ngaarumbidzwe.
\p
\v 48 Ndiye Mwari unonditsivira, Unondikundisa vanhu.
\p
\v 49 Unondibvisa kuvavengi vangu; Zvirokwazvo, munondisimudzira
\s kumusoro kwavanondimukira; Munondirwira pamunhu
\s unondimanikidza.
\p
\v 50 "Naizvozvo ndichakuvongai
\s Jehovha, pakati pendudzi,
\p Ndichakudza zita renyu nenziyo;
\v 51 Unopa mambo wake kuponeswa
\s kukuru;
\p Unoitira muzodzwa wake unyoro, Kuna Dhavhidhi navana vake nokusingaperi."
